    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. This example remains mechanically robust, with the critical VANOS system serviced and the rear subframe reinforced for enhanced torsional rigidity. The suspension utilizes a balanced MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, delivering precise turn-in and predictable lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the limited-slip differential and chassis dynamics remain sharp. A solid, performance-ready platform for the purist.",
