      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior finish maintains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find minor, honest road wear consistent with careful use. Mechanically, it is in excellent health; the engine pulls strong, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and it has a documented history of on-time fluid changes and preventative maintenance. Step inside to find a clean, smoke-free interior where the leather remains supple and the carpets are free of stains. Every feature, from the heated seats to the intuitive infotainment system, is fully operational. It sits on a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining and recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection. This is a solid, dependable car that looks great on the road and is ready for its next chapter.",
