    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via six individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated Double VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp gear synchronization, paired with a functional M-Variable differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to ensure structural rigidity, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventive maintenance to protect the crankshaft journals. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, offering the precise turn-in and communicative feedback expected of this chassis. This is a driver-focused example where performance-critical maintenance has been prioritized.",
